                        <interp inst="t18520920-name-466" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM GLADWIN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, R</hi> 122). I took this shirt off Bryant—Bryant said somebody had <hi rend="italic">come it</hi> on him—he said, "We got them out of the kitchen." (<hi rend="italic">Bryant was further charged with having been before convicted.</hi>)</p>
